sjp69d45.en:
Settlement Amount Calculation Formula (Deduction):
            Headquarters: (Transaction Amount - Service Fee) * Headquarters Settlement Ratio;
            Store: Order Amount - Service Fee - Headquarters Settlement Amount.
            External Deduction:
            Headquarters: Transaction Amount * Headquarters Settlement Ratio;
            Store: Order Amount - Headquarters Settlement Amount.

57ht306u.en:
Settlement amount calculation formula:
            Internal deduction:
            Headquarters: (Transaction amount - handling fee) * headquarters settlement ratio;
            Distributor: (Transaction amount - handling fee) * distributor settlement ratio;
            Store: Order amount - handling fee - headquarters settlement amount - distributor settlement amount.
            External deduction:
            Headquarters: Transaction amount * headquarters settlement ratio;
            Distributor: Transaction amount * distributor settlement ratio;
            Store: Order amount - headquarters settlement amount - distributor settlement amount.

